    ancRatingNum: 9.0,
    battery: "8h (24h case)",
    batteryNum: 8,
    price: 298,
    priceStr: "$298",
    codec: "SBC, AAC, LDAC",
    summary: "Sony packed their incredible noise cancellation and sound quality into a much smaller earbud form factor. These are arguably the most capable all-around true wireless earbuds available.",
