    batteryNum: 50,
    price: 299,
    priceStr: "$299",
    codec: "SBC, AAC",
    summary: "A strong mid-range contender, the JBL Tour One M2 offers excellent battery life, a comfortable fit, and highly customizable sound through their excellent companion app.",
